    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, looking as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, having been protected in a climate-controlled environment and treated with a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is pristine without a hint of UV exposure, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the seat heaters\u2014operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by certified technicians with a comprehensive folder of service records to prove it. The engine bay is spotless, the undercarriage is remarkably clean, and the tires are fresh. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the one. Single owner, non-smoker, clean title, and ready for its next caretaker.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
