    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered since day one. It drives like a dream and doesn't have a single mark on it. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and I promise you'll fall in love!",
      "price": 44900.0,
