    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system. This example delivers an uncompromising analog driving experience via its Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis integrity is superlative, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to preserve original torsional rigidity. Every mechanical component, from the MacPherson strut front suspension to the multi-link rear, functions with factory-fresh precision. Recent comprehensive service includes a critical valve clearance adjustment and a full cooling system overhaul, ensuring this naturally aspirated icon performs at its peak 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation.",
